(367, 'WHITE 3 has been suspended for two minutes. After leaving the court, but before the restart of the match, WHITE 3 is guilty of a seriously unsportsmanlike conduct in the substitution area against official B from BLACK team. Just before that, official B from BLACK team ran out onto the playing court, even though no permission had been given. No sanctions have been called against the officials of BLACK team. Correct decision?', '16', 9),
(368, 'When a player is disqualified, the team is reduced by 1 player on the court for 2 minutes, unless the disqualification is given:', '16', 10),
