(376, 'WHITE 4 is injured. The referees whistle for a time-out and give the hand signal to permit WHITE team to enter the court and take care of the player. Officials A and B from WHITE team, but also official A from BLACK team, enter the court. Official A from BLACK team already received a warning. Correct decision?', '16', 18),
